===============================================================================
第一条 维持经济结构与就业保障 (Economic Structure & Employment Maintenance)
===============================================================================

使用本系统必须以维持现有经济结构为前提。使用者须保证：

The use of this Work is conditional upon maintaining the existing economic
structure. Users shall ensure that:

  (a) 按其公司或工厂规模应配备的员工总数不得减少。
      The total number of employees required for the scale of the user's
      company or factory shall not be reduced.

  (b) 系统带来的效率提升只能用于增加员工数量，或在不降薪前提下减少员工
      工作时长，并保证对社会的税收贡献保持稳定。
      Productivity gains from the Work shall only be used to increase the
      number of employees, or to reduce working hours without loss of pay,
      while ensuring stable tax contributions to society.

  (c) 在满足上述 (a) 和 (b) 的基础之上，方可考虑使用本系统扩展市场规模。
      Market expansion using this Work is permitted ONLY after the above
      conditions (a) and (b) have been fulfilled.

===============================================================================
第二条 人类监督 (Human Oversight)
===============================================================================

本系统不得在完全剥夺人类监督与干预能力的模式下运行。部署本系统时，应当
确保人类始终保有对系统行为的知情权、干预权和最终决策权。

This Work shall not be operated in a mode that completely strips humans of
oversight and intervention capabilities. When deploying this Work, humans
shall always retain the right to be informed, to intervene, and to make
final decisions regarding the system's behavior.

===============================================================================
第三条 反资本剥削原则 (Anti-Exploitation Principles)
===============================================================================

我们反对将本系统用于加剧社会不平等的行为。我们倡导使用者在获取效率提升的同时，
将技术红利合理分配于社会价值创造，而非仅用于财富集中。

We oppose using this Work in ways that exacerbate social inequality. We
encourage users to distribute the technological dividends toward creating
social value, rather than solely concentrating wealth.

具体而言，我们期望使用者避免以下行为：

Specifically, we expect users to avoid the following:

  (a) 利用本系统获取的效率提升仅用于利润集中，而未合理回馈员工与社会。
      Concentrating productivity gains solely as profit without reasonably
      benefiting employees and society.

  (b) 利用本系统强化市场垄断地位，抑制公平竞争。
      Using this Work to reinforce monopolistic positions and suppress
      fair competition.

  (c) 利用本系统从事不产生实际经济价值的纯投机活动。
      Engaging in purely speculative activities that produce no real
      economic value.

  (d) 利用本系统的效率提升加重劳动者负担，而非改善其工作条件。
      Using productivity gains to intensify worker burden rather than
      improve working conditions.

