第四条 公约性质声明 (Nature of This Covenant)
===============================================================================

本公约为社区自愿遵循的价值承诺（Community Voluntary Commitment），不构成
对 Apache License 2.0 许可证的修改或补充，不产生独立的法律约束力。

This covenant is a Community Voluntary Commitment and does NOT constitute
a modification or supplement to the Apache License 2.0. It does not create
independent legal obligations.

任何人使用、修改、分发灵智 MindPal 智能体系统的权利，完整地受 Apache
License 2.0 保障，不因本公约而受到任何限制。

The rights of any person to use, modify, and distribute the MindPal agent
system are fully protected by the Apache License 2.0 and shall not be
restricted in any way by this covenant.

我们相信，技术进步应当服务于全人类的福祉，而非加剧不平等。我们期望每一位
社区成员在自身能力范围内践行本公约的精神。

We believe that technological progress should serve the well-being of all
humanity, not exacerbate inequality. We hope that every community member
will practice the spirit of this covenant within their own capabilities.

